extends layout

block content 
  h2 Become an admin 
  p Enter a valid admin key to become an admin.
  form(method="POST") 
    div.form-group
      label(for="key") Admin Key
      input(type="password", name="key", required)
    button(type="submit") Submit

  if errors 
      h3 Correct the following errors: 
      ul 
        each error in errors
          li!= error.msg
